lead_paragraph: If the Republicans gain control of the House of Representatives in Tuesday's election, as expected, attention shifts from the campaign trail to what the G.O.P. can do in practical terms to try to unravel pieces of the newly enacted health care overhaul.
snippet: Governors' races may also foretell state actions to set up insurance exchanges, implement individual mandates and review insurance rates.
abstract: Governors' races may also foretell state actions to set up insurance exchanges, implement individual mandates and review insurance rates.
